rComments: The course itself was easy. However, it is really discouraging when a professor at such a prestigious university does not even make an effort to try to pronounce even the simplest scientific names correctly.
Good professor, tests were fair and not too hard, but he seemed to just repeat what was a written on his slides.
great professor. very clear about what he expects the students to know for the exams. interesting lectures.

cares about students. tests are fair. approachable. nice guy. sense of humour. if u have him, sit at the front of the class. if you sit at the front, you will start to notice how passionate he is about what he teaches
